  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/41091dee512cd5691ecb65e7316d8842.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/41091dee512cd5691ecb65e7316d8842.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/41091dee512cd5691ecb65e7316d8842.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storage Looter is a loot game in a Voxel universe. Your goal is to collect the rarest and most profitable items in order to upgrade your store. Go open some boxes and resell your finds in your store, customers will soon come looking to buy a few treasures from you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/17548df12e43d4b511df1b93baa37831.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/17548df12e43d4b511df1b93baa37831.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/17548df12e43d4b511df1b93baa37831.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storage units, container yards, large halls, or parks, there are plenty of places to explore in search of the most profitable items. Try to collect the most valuable loot to upgrade your character and your shop. Search through furniture, cars, and grab whatever is worth the most!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/55cc769503db8fa284944bafcececbb8.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/55cc769503db8fa284944bafcececbb8.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/55cc769503db8fa284944bafcececbb8.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete missions with companies to make yourself known in the world of looting abandoned places. These companies will leave you free to come and go to different places, full of unique objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/dd7355154535b19279066d96c63d16a1.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/dd7355154535b19279066d96c63d16a1.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/dd7355154535b19279066d96c63d16a1.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only collect the essentials, your energy drops as you collect items and regenerates when you return home. This can be improved in order to collect more items per expedition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/ee707ad1cc0c8e2c2c9945fe61a65ec1.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/ee707ad1cc0c8e2c2c9945fe61a65ec1.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/ee707ad1cc0c8e2c2c9945fe61a65ec1.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Sell your finds and invest in upgrades for your shop, where you can showcase your rarest items! Buying furniture isn’t just for aesthetics, it also increases the value of the items you sell.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/41091dee512cd5691ecb65e7316d8842.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/41091dee512cd5691ecb65e7316d8842.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/41091dee512cd5691ecb65e7316d8842.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storage Looter is a loot game in a Voxel universe. Your goal is to collect the rarest and most profitable items in order to upgrade your store. Go open some boxes and resell your finds in your store, customers will soon come looking to buy a few treasures from you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/17548df12e43d4b511df1b93baa37831.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/17548df12e43d4b511df1b93baa37831.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/17548df12e43d4b511df1b93baa37831.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storage units, container yards, large halls, or parks, there are plenty of places to explore in search of the most profitable items. Try to collect the most valuable loot to upgrade your character and your shop. Search through furniture, cars, and grab whatever is worth the most!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/55cc769503db8fa284944bafcececbb8.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/55cc769503db8fa284944bafcececbb8.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/55cc769503db8fa284944bafcececbb8.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete missions with companies to make yourself known in the world of looting abandoned places. These companies will leave you free to come and go to different places, full of unique objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/dd7355154535b19279066d96c63d16a1.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/dd7355154535b19279066d96c63d16a1.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/dd7355154535b19279066d96c63d16a1.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only collect the essentials, your energy drops as you collect items and regenerates when you return home. This can be improved in order to collect more items per expedition.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/ee707ad1cc0c8e2c2c9945fe61a65ec1.poster.avif?t=1764086260\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/ee707ad1cc0c8e2c2c9945fe61a65ec1.webm?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784440/extras/ee707ad1cc0c8e2c2c9945fe61a65ec1.mp4?t=1764086260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Sell your finds and invest in upgrades for your shop, where you can showcase your rarest items! Buying furniture isn’t just for aesthetics, it also increases the value of the items you sell.</p>",
